name: Dubai (iOS10-12)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
Normal size. Install 'Dubai_85% (iOS10-12)' for smaller character size

Compatible with iOS10-12. Separate packages for iOS10-12 and iOS13 are available.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet

1.1: Fixed “ᴇ” on iOS12.4 - Pre-iOS12.4 users do NOT need to upgrade
